<title>Restore a backup</title>

  <p>If you have lost or deleted some of your files, but you have a backup of
  them, you can restore them from the backup.</p>

  <p>If you want to restore your backup from a device such as an
  external hard drive, USB drive or another computer on the network, you can
  <link xref="files-copy">copy them</link> back to your computer.</p>

